    <h1>Multiplayer UNO Online — Play With Friends or Strangers</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Create a room and share the link with friends, or join a public game with strangers. No downloads, no signups.</p>

    <h2>Real-Time Multiplayer</h2>
    <p>Our game uses WebSocket technology for instant, lag-free communication. Every card play, draw, and UNO call is synchronized across all players in real-time. There's no page refreshing, no waiting — just seamless gameplay.</p>

    <h2>3 Ways to Play Together</h2>
    <h3>1. Private Rooms</h3>
    <p>Create a private room and share the room code or invite link with your friends. Only people with the code can join — perfect for friend groups and family.</p>

    <h3>2. Public Rooms</h3>
    <p>Create a public room and it appears in the room browser. Anyone can join and play — the easiest way to play UNO online with strangers when your friends aren't around. Great for meeting new opponents and playing pickup games.</p>

    <h3>3. Invite Links</h3>
    <p>One-click invite links work on any platform. Share via WhatsApp, Discord, iMessage, email, or any messaging app. Friends tap the link and they're in the game.</p>

    <h2>Host Controls</h2>
    <p>The room host has full control over the game experience:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Start & Restart</strong> — Begin new rounds whenever you're ready</li>
      <li><strong>Kick Players</strong> — Remove disruptive players at any time</li>
      <li><strong>Toggle Stacking</strong> — Enable or disable card stacking rules</li>
      <li><strong>Reorder Seats</strong> — Arrange the playing order before starting</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Reconnection & AFK</h2>
    <p>Life happens. If you disconnect, your cards are preserved on the server and you'll automatically reconnect when you return. If a player is AFK for 30 seconds, the game plays for them so nobody is left waiting.</p>

    <h2>Spectator Mode</h2>
    <p>Game already started? No problem. Join as a spectator and watch the action unfold. You'll see all public game state — cards on the table, player card counts, and who's winning.</p>

    <h2>Supported Configurations</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>2 to 20 players per room</li>
      <li>Automatic double-deck for 11+ players</li>
      <li>Works on any device with a modern browser</li>
      <li>No app installation required</li>
      <li>Free — no premium tiers or paywalls</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="cta-banner">
      <h3>Start a Multiplayer Game Now</h3>
      <p>Create a room and send the invite link. Your friends will be playing in seconds.</p>
      <a href="/play" class="btn btn-hero">Play Multiplayer UNO</a>
    </div>
  </div>
